ultiplication restriction of rules`                (round2; always-on)\n65:Round-2 ordering evidence: comb1 -> `Unbound, Fresh public constants,\n67:Formula guardedness, Lemma annotations, Multiplication restriction, Nat Sorts,\n68:Subterm`; diff_mega/diff_place -> `... Reserved names, Reserved prefixes,\n69:Fr facts, ... lhs-not-rhs, Left/Right rule, Formula terms, ...`.\n76:variables (#1) and Fresh public constants (#2) are emitted before the\n81:Gated on `theory.is_diff`: `Reserved prefixes`, `Left rule`, `Right rule`\n83:nothing). Always-on (both modes): `Fresh public constants`, `Lemma\n84:annotations`, `Multiplication restriction of rules`.\n151:### Fresh public constants (round2; always-on)\n160:### Reserved prefixes (round2; DIFF MODE ONLY)\n165:The HEADER is word-filled (Wadler `fillSep`) at WIDTH 69, indent 2 (measured via\n167:exceed 69). Words treat the rule name `\\`NAME'` and each of `('DiffIntr',` /\n169:    \"    <fact_pp>\\n    (ProtoFact <Mult> \\\"<name>\\\" <arity>,<arity>,<Mult>)\"\n174:### Left rule / Right rule (round2; DIFF MODE ONLY)\n176:whose explicit `left`/`right` projection differs from the parent rule projected\n177:to that side (`diff(a,b)` -> a on left, -> b on right). Per rule the LEFT\n178:projection is tested first; if inconsistent the RIGHT is not reported for that\n179:rule (probe diff_both: both sides bad -> only \"Left rule\"). Body per entry\n183:(\"left\"/\"right\" and topic \"Left rule\"/\"Right rule\"). Consistency compared via\n184:the projected vs. explicit fact lists. Left rule topic precedes Right rule.\n186:### Lemma annotations (round2; always-on)\n192:### Multiplication restriction of rules (round2; always-on)\n245:Used by Left/Right rule and Multiplication restriction. Base form (single line","is_error":false}]},"uuid":"3d1978f2-de93-436c-a436-2ae47631cb20","timestamp":"2026-07-17T12:22:02.349Z","toolUseResult":{"stdout":"=== probe labels in QUERIES.log ===\n70:z3_sources :: exists-trace [sources] -> SUCCESS\n83:ro